{"tid":353542,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)《Despacito》的粵語版","createTime":"2017-08-09T16:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T17:30:51.000Z","uid":131293,"like":70,"dislike":116,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0278eea187936279287adbaf8438c1dae7a6a1a5","tid":353542,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:24:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj&amp;utm_campaign=topic_ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj&amp;utm_medium=share&amp;utm_source=clipboard_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3DABFGD1owBwNZEwNj%26utm_campaign%3Dtopic_ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj%26utm_medium%3Dshare%26utm_source%3Dclipboard_share&d=t4nFgH9TD0C6R7MlJds7ro9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d99cd7ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj&amp;utm_campaign=topic_ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj&amp;utm_medium=share&amp;utm_source=clipboard_share</a><br />\nLuis Fonsi與Daddy Yankee於今年1月推出的西班牙語歌曲《Despacito》，短短七個月已經有超過30億點擊率，成為Youtube最高點擊影片。而本地創作歌手Hinry劉卓軒最近亦與Beatboxer&nbsp;Heartgrey&nbsp;合作，推出《Despacito》的粵語版。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙語《Despacito》解作慢一點、慢慢來的意思，原版被指是18禁歌曲，因為歌詞不少內容都有情慾暗示，<span style=\"color: blue;\">當中的「慢」亦充滿色情的意思</span>。而這個廣東話版的《Despacito》，則是在講[red]「慢」是一種生活態度red]，不要只看事件最終的成敗，要享受中間的過程，過程中的意義更重要。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n歌詞節錄：&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n「Despacito<br />\n<br />\n慢慢地跟節奏擺舞怎會不妥<br />\n<br />\n落幕時刻伸手總可隨便點播<br />\n<br />\n誰人躊躇誰人難過需要幫助」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n「慢 係一種速度 同時係一種生活態度<br />\n<br />\n欣賞風景沿路 停低腳步<br />\n<br />\n人哋話 志不可慢 時不可失<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得 寧可放慢不可錯失」<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/912nhyp5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F912nhyp5&h=4f057263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就咁聽都算順口<br />\n我就覺得改咗歌嘅內容冇咁好<br />\n不過都係講緊香港人嘅生活態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：支持香港嘅創作<br />\n<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e16d7f810bd6176edc23d0acc55efec00fcb06","tid":353542,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而這個廣東話版的《Despacito》，則是在講「慢」是一種生活態度，不要只看事件最終的成敗，要享受中間的過程，過程中的意義更重要。&nbsp;</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Quote多次靚嘅"},{"pid":"72c3e28ff9f4f7e7e2704dd386e8ddd2ed46a217","tid":353542,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj&amp;utm_campaign=topic_ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj&amp;utm_medium=share&amp;utm_source=clipboard_share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3DABFGD1owBwNZEwNj%26utm_campaign%3Dtopic_ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj%26utm_medium%3Dshare%26utm_source%3Dclipboard_share&d=t4nFgH9TD0C6R7MlJds7ro9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d99cd7ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj&amp;utm_campaign=topic_ABFGD1owBwNZEwNj&amp;utm_medium=share&amp;utm_source=clipboard_share</a><br />\n<br />\n補Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68b8de716f69538f07b380d9dabcf4c41a9627c","tid":353542,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:36:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5ce92e9c9131452065b04b022d8e83342d38c2","tid":353542,"uid":131293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17ccd471e5265448e5f527cd929a316e7be92fb","tid":353542,"uid":20302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T16:39:25.000Z","ms